description: Demolition of existing buildings and erection of a development comprising two basement levels with three 6 storey blocks above ground, linked by lower four storey elements. All to provide a mixed use development comprising 65 residential units consisting of 36 affordable housing units (comprising 8 x 1-bed, 11 x 2-bed, 6 x 3-bed, and 11 x 4-bed) and 29 private housing units (comprising 5 x 1-bed, 5 x 2-bed, 6 x 3-bed and 13 x 4-bed), and 1791sqm of conference floorspace (Class D2), 760sqm of retail floorspace (Class A1), 46 car parking spaces (including 9 disabled spaces) and 118 cycle spaces at basement level, refuse storage, amenity space and landscaping.
